          "content": {
            "size": 4222,
            "mimeType": "text/html;charset=UTF-8",
            "compression": 0,
            "text": "<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"pt-br\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <title>Lista de Usuários</title>\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/main.css\"/>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div><header id=\"site-header\">\r\n    <div class=\"header-left\"></div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"header-center\">\r\n        <h1>☕ Spring Espresso Game Testing</h1>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"header-right\">\r\n        <form action=\"/logout\" method=\"post\" class=\"logout\">\r\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"button button-secondary\">Sair</button>\r\n        </form>\r\n    </div>\r\n</header></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n    <h1>Gerenciar Usuários</h1>\r\n\r\n    \r\n    \r\n\r\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\r\n        <a href=\"/usuarios/novo\" class=\"button button-primary\">Novo Usuário</a>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"table-container\">\r\n        <table class=\"data-table\">\r\n            <thead>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                    <th>ID</th>\r\n                    <th>Nome</th>\r\n                    <th>Email</th>\r\n                    <th>Perfil</th>\r\n                    <th>Ações</th>\r\n                </tr>\r\n            </thead>\r\n            <tbody>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                    <td>1</td>\r\n                    <td>Admin</td>\r\n                    <td>admin@admin.com</td>\r\n                    <td>\r\n                        <span style=\"color: #d32f2f; font-weight: bold;\">\r\n                            🔐 Administrador\r\n                        </span>\r\n                        \r\n                    </td>\r\n                    <td class=\"actions\">\r\n                        <a href=\"/usuarios/detalhes/1\" class=\"button button-secondary\">Ver detalhes</a>\r\n                        <a href=\"/usuarios/editar/1\" class=\"button button-secondary\">Editar</a>\r\n                        <a href=\"/usuarios/remover/1\" \r\n                           class=\"button button-secondary\"\r\n                           onclick=\"return confirm('Tem certeza que deseja remover este usuário?')\">Remover</a>\r\n                    </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                    <td>2</td>\r\n                    <td>Maria Silva</td>\r\n                    <td>user@user.com</td>\r\n                    <td>\r\n                        \r\n                        <span style=\"color: #1976d2; font-weight: bold;\">\r\n                            👤 Usuário\r\n                        </span>\r\n                    </td>\r\n                    <td class=\"actions\">\r\n                        <a href=\"/usuarios/detalhes/2\" class=\"button button-secondary\">Ver detalhes</a>\r\n                        <a href=\"/usuarios/editar/2\" class=\"button button-secondary\">Editar</a>\r\n                        <a href=\"/usuarios/remover/2\" \r\n                           class=\"button button-secondary\"\r\n                           onclick=\"return confirm('Tem certeza que deseja remover este usuário?')\">Remover</a>\r\n                    </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                <tr>\r\n                    <td>3</td>\r\n                    <td>User Usuario</td>\r\n                    <td>useruser@user.com</td>\r\n                    <td>\r\n                        \r\n                        <span style=\"color: #1976d2; font-weight: bold;\">\r\n                            👤 Usuário\r\n                        </span>\r\n                    </td>\r\n                    <td class=\"actions\">\r\n                        <a href=\"/usuarios/detalhes/3\" class=\"button button-secondary\">Ver detalhes</a>\r\n                        <a href=\"/usuarios/editar/3\" class=\"button button-secondary\">Editar</a>\r\n                        <a href=\"/usuarios/remover/3\" \r\n                           class=\"button button-secondary\"\r\n                           onclick=\"return confirm('Tem certeza que deseja remover este usuário?')\">Remover</a>\r\n                    </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n                \r\n            </tbody>\r\n        </table>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"navigation-section\">\r\n    <a href=\"/\" class=\"button button-secondary\">Voltar ao Home</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<footer>\r\n    <p>Spring Espresso Game Testing. Um Software Open-source para a disciplina de Desenvolvimento Web.</p>\r\n    <p>Desenvolvido com café e paixão!</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</footer>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>"
