          "content": {
            "size": 2975,
            "mimeType": "text/html;charset=UTF-8",
            "compression": 0,
            "text": "<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"pt-br\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <title>Novo Usuário</title>\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/main.css\"/>\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/form.css\"/>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div><header id=\"site-header\">\r\n    <div class=\"header-left\"></div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"header-center\">\r\n        <h1>☕ Spring Espresso Game Testing</h1>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"header-right\">\r\n        <form action=\"/logout\" method=\"post\" class=\"logout\">\r\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"button button-secondary\">Sair</button>\r\n        </form>\r\n    </div>\r\n</header></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n    <h1>Novo Usuário</h1>\r\n\r\n    \r\n\r\n    <form action=\"/usuarios/salvar\" method=\"post\">\r\n        <input type=\"hidden\" id=\"id\" name=\"id\" value=\"\">\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"form-section\">\r\n            <h3>Informações do Usuário</h3>\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n                <label for=\"nome\">Nome Completo *</label>\r\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"nome\" placeholder=\"Digite o nome completo\" required maxlength=\"255\" name=\"nome\" value=\"\">\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n                <label for=\"email\">Email *</label>\r\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" placeholder=\"Digite o email\" required maxlength=\"255\" name=\"email\" value=\"\">\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n                <label for=\"senha\">Senha</label>\r\n                <input type=\"password\" id=\"senha\" placeholder=\"Digite a senha\" \r\n                       minlength=\"6\" required=\"required\" name=\"senha\" value=\"\">\r\n                \r\n                <small style=\"color: #666;\">\r\n                    Mínimo 6 caracteres\r\n                </small>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"form-group\">\r\n                <label for=\"role\">Perfil de Acesso *</label>\r\n                <select id=\"role\" required name=\"role\">\r\n                    <option value=\"\">Selecione um perfil</option>\r\n                    <option value=\"ROLE_ADMIN\">Administrador</option>\r\n                    <option value=\"ROLE_USER\">Usuário</option>\r\n                </select>\r\n                <small style=\"color: #666;\">\r\n                    <strong>Administrador:</strong> Acesso total ao sistema<br>\r\n                    <strong>Usuário:</strong> Acesso limitado às funcionalidades básicas\r\n                </small>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"form-actions\">\r\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"button button-primary\">\r\n                <span>Criar Usuário</span>\r\n            </button>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </form>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"navigation-section\">\r\n    <a href=\"/usuarios\" class=\"button button-secondary\">Cancelar</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<footer>\r\n    <p>Spring Espresso Game Testing. Um Software Open-source para a disciplina de Desenvolvimento Web.</p>\r\n    <p>Desenvolvido com café e paixão!</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</footer>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>"
          },
